com.example.hello.impl

Interface HelloCommand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.lightbend.lagom.serialization.Jsonable, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HelloCommand.Hello, HelloCommand.UseGreetingMessage

    public interface HelloCommand
extends com.lightbend.lagom.serialization.Jsonable
    This interface defines all the commands that the HelloEntity supports.

    By convention, the commands should be inner classes of the interface, which makes it simple to get a complete picture of what commands an entity supports.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  HelloCommand.Hello
